  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>There's plenty on offer in the mornings to get you fueled up for a day on the slopes, with a hot and cold breakfast buffet.</p>
<p>On half board you can enjoy a four course meal each evening with a salad buffet, choice of main and dessert buffet to finish.</p>
<p>If you're not on half-board you'll get a discount in various mountain restaurants, including La Motta and La Salette. Guests also receive discount at the hotel's a la carte restaurant Mon Amour which offers great home-made pastas and desserts.</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala meals included. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
