  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms </strong>sleep up to two people with a double or twin beds and have a bath or shower.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Twin Rooms </strong>sleep up to three people using a single sofa bed. They have a balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms </strong>are available without a supplement. They have a shower.</p>
<p><strong>Twin Rooms for sole use</strong> are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p>If you would like your beds pushed together and made up as a double bed, a request must be made at time of booking.</p>
